sentences.english: The leading cause of dental implant failures are infections following a dental implant.
sentences.chinese: 领先的种植牙失败的原因是感染后牙种植体。

sentences.english: The number of implants is determined by the specific requirements of each case.
sentences.chinese: 种植体的数量取决于每个患者的条件。

sentences.english: Objective To discuss the clinical nursing gist of immediate implanting of ITI implant.
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨ITI种植体即刻种植的临床护理要点。

sentences.english: Objective To study clinical application of implant-supported magnetic attachment retained complete overdentures.
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨种植体磁性附着体固位全口义齿的临床应用。

sentences.english: Osseointegration is a prerequisite for successful dental or orthopaedic implants.
sentences.chinese: 组织形成骨结合是种植体成功的前提。

sentences.english: The placement of dental implants can be of interest for many patients.
sentences.chinese: 种植体的放置对于许多患者是有利的。

sentences.english: Implant retained prostheses may not be most suitable treatment option for many patients.
sentences.chinese: 对很多患者而言，种植体支持的修复体也并不适宜。

sentences.english: The stability of saw-toothed thread implants is better than "V"thread.
sentences.chinese: 锯齿型螺纹种植体的稳定性比三角型螺纹好。

sentences.english: Objective To study the stability of micro-implant anchorage which were loaded immediately.
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨微型支抗种植体即刻加力的稳定性。

sentences.english: The study and the application of anchorage implants had attracted more and more attention from the orthodontists .
sentences.chinese: 支抗种植体是近年来国内外正畸学研究的热点之一。

sentences.english: Objective To compare the stress distribution of implant in maxillary complex in anterior, medium and posterior postions under vertical and horizontal loading.
sentences.chinese: 目的讨论种植体在上颌骨复合体中的生物力学行为。

sentences.english: A failed osseointegration process means that the dental implant is unsuccessful.
sentences.chinese: 失败的骨整合的过程意味著牙种植体是不成功的。

sentences.english: Titanium alloy implants were placed in the medial aspect of the tibial metaphysis.
sentences.chinese: 钛合金种植体植入胫骨干骺端的前内侧面。

sentences.english: The glabella region is not optimal but an alternative option for nasal implants.
sentences.chinese: 眉间点作为种植体植入部位应慎重。

sentences.english: Remember that dental implants put your health on the line.
sentences.chinese: 请记住，把你的健康牙种植体上线。

sentences.english: The distance between mesial and distal implants should also be considered.
sentences.chinese: 同时在位置设计中注意控制种植体间的距离。

definition: to have a false tooth set in/denture
